 "base_path": "/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam70120",
 "body": "<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Many forms and help sheets can be downloaded online at Gov.UK. This is the preferred route for customers to take.&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">For example,<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW46426401 BCX8\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/find-hmrc-contacts/self-assessment-forms-ordering\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Self-Assessment: forms ordering - GOV.UK</span></span></a><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">However, order line can be used by customers to order supplementary pages or guidance which has not been enclosed with their paper tax return.&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Leaflets or Help Sheets mentioned in the Tax Return Guide can also be ordered from the Order line.</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Contacting<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Orderline</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">:-</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"ListContainerWrapper SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><ul class=\"BulletListStyle1 SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><li class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Telephone: 0300 200 3610</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"ListContainerWrapper SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><ul class=\"BulletListStyle1 SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><li class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Outside UK: +44 161 930 8331</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">Opening times: Monday to Friday: 8am to 5pm. Closed </span></span><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW46426401 BCX8\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/bank-holidays\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">bank holidays</span></span></a><span class=\"TextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW46426401 BCX8\">.</span></span><span class=\"EOP Selected SCXW46426401 BCX8\">&nbsp;</span></p></div>\n",
